&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_block&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&lt;em data-stringify-type=&quot;italic&quot;&gt;IMPORTANT NOTICE: Our company takes the security and privacy of job applicants very seriously. We will never ask for payment, bank details, or personal financial information as part of the application process. All our legitimate job postings can be found on our official career site. Please be cautious of job offers that come from non-company email addresses (@klaviyo.com), instant messaging platforms, or unsolicited calls.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;By clicking &quot;Submit Application&quot; you consent to Klaviyo processing your Personal Data in accordance with our Job Applicant Privacy Notice.&amp;nbsp; If you do not wish for Klaviyo to process your Personal Data, please do not submit an application.&lt;em data-stringify-type=&quot;italic&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em data-stringify-type=&quot;italic&quot;&gt;You can find our Job Applicant Privacy Notice&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em data-stringify-type=&quot;italic&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.klaviyo.com/legal/job-applicant-privacy-notice&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.klaviyo.com/legal/job-applicant-privacy-notice&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em data-stringify-type=&quot;italic&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.klaviyo.com/fr/legal/job-applicant-privacy-notice&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; (FR).&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
